<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-3"></div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
  <h1>WELCOME TO ZENBREW</h1>
  <h4>A place for homebrewers to save and organize their recipes</h4>
  <br>

  <p><button type="button" class="btn-warning btn-lg btn-info" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#signUpModal">Get started now!</button></p>
  <br>

  <p>Being passionate about homebrewing is a breeze, but staying organized can be a challenge. Instead of fumbling with complicated spreadsheets or paying big bucks for fancy software, try our website for free! (That's about how much you've budgeted for logging your recipes, right?) Create an account, save your brew recipes, and come back anytime to see how far you've come as a brewer. You won't regret it!</p><br><br>
